 ## Zide Payment Service
 ### Overview
 
+Status: This repository is currently a scaffold and is not the active runtime payment API in this workspace.
+
+Active payment and wallet processing currently runs in:
+- zide-backend-jobs-service (job payment orchestration and settlement queue)
+- zide-backend-auth-service (wallet/reward operations)
+
+Until this service is fully implemented and integrated, use the active services above for payment-related APIs.
+
 >> The Zide Payment Service is a microservice designed to handle all payment processing tasks for the Zide platform. It supports integration with multiple payment gateways, provides secure transaction management, and includes features such as transaction logging and refund processing.
 
